OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FScattered
OL,6,Fshowers continuing overnight with some
OL,7,Fclearer spells in between. Showers
OL,8,Fperhaps becoming more organised and
OL,9,Fheavier later in the night with a
OL,10,Fstronger breeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA day of sunny spells and
OL,13,Fscattered showers, with some heavier
OL,14,Fshowers possible. Cloud building later
OL,15,Fwith some wet and windy weather
OL,16,Farriving by evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
